      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOOGIE MCGRAW (5) is progressing well scoring last time out (25.28) at this track and bringing up his 3rd career win. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of three tries. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In top form and looks a key chance again. ROLLING IN MUD (3) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 10 lengths (25.15). Looks suited and is one of the contenders. BARCIA CRUISER (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (25.89) at this track behind ROLLING IN MUD in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Winning chance. ZIPPING BJORN (7) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
